headline: Huntington Bank Names Eric Wasserstrom Executive Vice President, Head of Investor Relations
summary: The Huntington National Bank (Huntington) is pleased to announce Eric Wasserstrom has joined as Executive Vice President, Head of Investor Relations, effective April 28.

headline: Huntington ahead of schedule on Carolinas expansion, CFO says
summary: The bank has 37 of the 55 branches it plans to open in North and South Carolina under letter of intent for real estate development, Huntington CFO Zach Wasserman said.
